description:
&lt;p&gt;The Estates Department is responsible for the repair, maintenance and management of all Building and Engineering Services within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an experienced Craftsperson (Mechanical) to join our multi-disciplined Estates Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be time served and have a mechanical background and will be responsible for the provision of engineering maintenance services primarily for the Trust owned buildings within the Teesside locality of the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although primarily based at Roseberry Park Hospital, Middlesbrough you may be required to work from other Trust sites for periods of time as the service dictates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Graham Nellis - Senior Estates Officer - 07881262345&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
